director of Android Wear, Dave

00:00:08.180 --> 00:00:08.940
Singleton.

00:00:08.940 --> 00:00:10.726
Hi, Dave, thank you
for joining us today.

00:00:10.726 --> 00:00:12.100
DAVID SINGLETON:
It's a pleasure.

00:00:12.100 --> 00:00:14.624
