keynote this morning.

00:00:16.540 --> 00:00:18.160
I was wondering if
you could tell us,

00:00:18.160 --> 00:00:19.784
what are some of the
biggest highlights

00:00:19.784 --> 00:00:21.050
from your perspective?

00:00:21.050 --> 00:00:23.174
DAVID SINGLETON: Yes, so
today's been really great.

00:00:23.174 --> 00:00:25.270
This is our second time
as part of the keynote

00:00:25.270 --> 00:00:28.190
at Google I/O. Last
year, obviously,

00:00:28.190 --> 00:00:31.110
